    "en": {
      "title": "President Ranil's oath in Parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, who was elected as the new President, announced in the Parliament that he will be sworn in as the President.",
        "Accordingly, he said that he will take oath in the Parliament complex outside the House.",
        "Also, President Ranil Wickramasinghe asked all members of the Parliament to join together for the sake of building the country."
      ],
